{"tid":309743,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NAS專用HDD同普通HDD","createTime":"2017-07-05T09:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T16:47:40.000Z","uid":24137,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07a97b146f7f12d2000535f27b020f0573e51929","tid":309743,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:45:58.000Z","msg":"想問呢兩款HDD真係有作為??<br />\n<br />\n數據上普通HDD行5x8 專用HDD行7x24  實際壽命真係差咁遠？<br />\n共振方面專用HDD真係比普通HDD做得好？ <br />\n讀寫容錯方面專用HDD真係比普通HDD做得好?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申：考慮緊買NAS HDD, 想收集下意見。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲NAS用緊咩HDD ??<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專用HDD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通HDD"},{"pid":"84a9cd14bac2925ef8cd64268dc2e810527e13b6","tid":309743,"uid":87120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"咩HDD 都會死<br />\n<br />\nNAS HD 一年就死又有<br />\n普通HD 用左 5 年都未死又有<br />\n<br />\n所以都係多重 Backup 穩陣！<br />\n<br />\nNAS 行 RAID 1 ， 死左咪即再ReBluid 過囉"},{"pid":"e6264b561cf8f5a2da563d1c0aa65454cae2a2a3","tid":309743,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩HDD 都會死<br />\n<br />\nNAS HD 一年就死又有<br />\n普通HD 用左 5 年都未死又有<br />\n<br />\n所以都係多重 Backup 穩陣！<br />\n<br />\nNAS 行 RAID 1 ， 死左咪即再ReBluid 過囉</blockquote><br />\n我有行raid1，純粹好奇呢兩種有咩分別，專用hdd初岀果陣都覺得技術上應該穩陣啲，但事隔咁多年又覺得普通hdd應該追上"},{"pid":"cb223879cddca57a45edd28436b1ede63aac01a8","tid":309743,"uid":30724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:28:20.000Z","msg":"淘寶 320gb wd <br />\n用左3年，仲未壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe4e084dbf0590da48328b2881e68ff1660de3a","tid":309743,"uid":30724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淘寶 320gb wd <br />\n用左3年，仲未壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用黎放大陸野，80＄人仔"},{"pid":"3fb96517179f775d39f48d2b5b0c30a925efb03e","tid":309743,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩HDD 都會死<br />\n<br />\nNAS HD 一年就死又有<br />\n普通HD 用左 5 年都未死又有<br />\n<br />\n所以都係多重 Backup 穩陣！<br />\n<br />\nNAS 行 RAID 1 ， 死左咪即再ReBluid 過囉</blockquote><br />\n我有行raid1，純粹好奇呢兩種有咩分別，專用hdd初岀果陣都覺得技術上應該穩陣啲，但事隔咁多年又覺得普通hdd應該追上</blockquote><br />\n兩樣野冇關係"},{"pid":"710ceb4161315052df62ea8757b4689fc8be57b6","tid":309743,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"個道理就好似intel垃圾igp過左幾多代都係垃圾一樣"},{"pid":"2f5d8a3126a5471925fa16e80997a724cb29593b","tid":309743,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分別可能只係某個parts用所謂好D既料咁解<br />\n眼睇係電路上兩隻野用料一樣，分別可能只係所謂NAS級個啤鈴靚D掛"}]}